only reflect commercial, external activities.** The substantial launch capacity used internally for the Connectivity segment (and in the future, for the AI segment) is treated as a capital investment within those respective segments. This results in the Space segment having "relatively lower revenue scale and revenue growth" compared to its actual operational output, as its foundational value is embedded in the growth of the other segments.',
